Calolydella virginiajamesae
has been reared 34 times from various species of 
Lepidoptera
from several families (
Nymphalidae
; 
Hesperiidae
; 
Lycaenidae
; 
Geometridae
; 
Crambidae
; 
Erebidae
; 
Riodinidae
; 
Sphingidae
; and 
Pieridae
), in rain forest, cloud forest, dry forest, and dry-rain lowland intergrade ecosystems.
